#25500
Manhattan~
As you drive across the Brooklyn bridge you can see the great island of 
Manhattan. As you drive across the bridge you can see to the west the 
famous clock tower, that is home to the police station.  As you drive 
further along you can just make out the weird house to the south, it is 
rumored that the person that lives there hasn't come out for years and
has never been seen by the few houses that are close enough to see the
front of it. To the east you can see The Xanatos building that has recently
acquired a castle on top of it. The castle cost a lot of money to move and
David Xanatos never would give a reason to the putting of it on top of the 
worlds largest building. Because of the mystery behind the case you think
that you should go ask Xanatos first and then head over to the police
station to see what other clues you can dig up.
