man spares no expense in his buildings. There is a massive desk by the wall 
with a lazy guard behind it. You can see by the video camera's on the walls 
that no  one would ever break into this build and make it to the top. As you 
walk forward to the elevator the guard greets you and asks what you are 
doing here. After some explaining you finally convince the guard that you 
are really who you  say and he waves you on saying "Mr. Xanatos is waiting."
